props.name: model
props.description: The model that the select value syncs to

props.name: options
props.description: The option data of the select

props.name: defaultKey
props.description: The value attribute of the default option

props.name: defaultValue
props.description: The label attribute of the default option

events.name: change
events.description: Dispatched when the select is changed (return option[optionKey])

events.name: selected
events.description: Dispatched when the select is selected (return option)
